{"word":"ναυάγιον","slug":"ναυάγιον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ναυάγιον</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a piece of wreck</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>ναυάγια ἱππικά</el> <i>the wreck</i> of a chariot, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>= <a href='S:ναυαγία'><el>ναυαγία</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Strabo'>Strab.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>ναυᾱγός</el>\n"}]}